{
  "stem": "23730.3",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "His name was Pinter, who was a very popular man in the camp.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And he pulled me away from these people.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I wouldn't be sitting here otherwise.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "They would have killed me there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "He tore me away from the people.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Don't touch that man.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "That's the best-behaved prisoner in the whole camp.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "I vouch for that man.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Let me just deal with him.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And so I survived that queuing up for another plate of soup.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "It gives you insight of-- of the life of a concentration camp, of a good concentration camp, a-- where things were quite normal, I mean, if the word is appropriate for that.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Sure there was.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Every morning, practically, the flogging and beatings by kapos.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "A lot of beatings were done by Messinger.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And there was one morning when he was beating a young 16-, 17-year-old And he held back.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He held back.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was obvious he was holding back.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He was not beating.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And Schwarz got hold of Messinger.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "If you don't beat-- you see, I can't-- I notice that you are not beating properly.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "You will get it unless you start beating properly.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And still, Messinger did not beat properly that young boy.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But certainly, when other kapos did the flogging, then it was terrible.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "There was hanging in the camp, hanging.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "If somebody tried to run away, which was impossible, but just the attempt, right, or  moved out, he got a big, red circle on his back on the pajama.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And that was-- meant he is condemned to death, to hanging.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And that's how sometimes weeks went by.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And he knew he was going to hanged.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And he was amongst us.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Unbelievable.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
